title: Week 7 Studs & Duds + Field of Screams, Ja’Marvelous Chase - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/25
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 7! With so many elite players on bye, who stepped up, and who was the most disappointing? What are the latest Tua Tagovailoa trade rumors? Plus, injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 25th, 2021.
  
 (02:15) - Monday Punday
 (04:20) - NFL News
 (10:00) - Fantasy Studmuffins
 (10:10) - QB Studs
 (24:05) - RB Studs
 (35:05) - WR Studs
 (40:30) - TE Studs
 (45:40) - Fantasy Duds
 (46:00) - QB Duds
 (48:15) - RB Duds
 (53:00) - WR Duds
 (54:30) - TE Duds
